<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="8a797c6e7d997b2ee1e2b49e">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=8fa59e02&authorId=632fc520d02ae1e217bfbb21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/78310a55b319ebc4e4c8dfea8f26cffc1e171614.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>浩然文史</strong>
<span>文史类学者、博士团队，让专业的历史更有趣。</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=8a797c6e7d997b2ee1e2b49e&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/0824ab18972bd407ffa1ec9876899e510fb30974.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
霜叶红于二月花：二十四节气之霜降，你该知道的气候和民俗
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=8a797c6e7d997b2ee1e2b49e&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
霜降是秋季的最后一个节气。霜降之后，秋天正式结束，寒冷的冬季就要来了。霜降有三候：一候豺乃祭兽；二候草木黄落；三候蜇虫咸俯。霜降前后的气候逐渐萧索和肃杀，相应的民俗也充满肃杀之气。不过，这一片肃杀中也有一抹亮色，那就是漫山的红叶。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-10-23</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">818</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="02c9b57397509bdc821a99a7">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=7f91c182&authorId=0c0eaf1e44dbd14fb72e1c20&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/fd039245d688d43f0420e430711ed21b0ff43b62.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>热点说</strong>
<span>时事热点，尽情分享</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=02c9b57397509bdc821a99a7&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/4034970a304e251f1261f4abac86c9177e3e53ca.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
霜降，一年最后的秋天
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=02c9b57397509bdc821a99a7&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
2017年10月23日，进入二十四节气中的霜降。霜降节气含有天气渐冷、初霜出现的意思，是秋季的最后一个节气，也意味着冬天即将开始。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-10-23</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">510</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="242a1308b48fefde401c459c">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=51ae9ff3&authorId=061aa7ee6640bbb08b38b021&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/1f178a82b9014a9055c8267fa5773912b21bee7a.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>非遗大数据</strong>
<span>传播非物质文化遗产</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=242a1308b48fefde401c459c&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/79f0f736afc379311db66649e6c4b74542a911f7.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
霜打的茄子，别就知道吃！
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=242a1308b48fefde401c459c&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
“秋风萧瑟天气凉，草木摇落露为霜”，每年阳历10月23日前后，当太阳到达黄经210度时，秋天的最后一个节气——霜降，就带着清冷之气款款而至了。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-10-21</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">50</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="e3ce1325332e74e731416fd0">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1f5ded52&authorId=cbfa87f1ee8beae383e2e326&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b3fb43166d224f4a1965b2ca05f790529922d16f.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>古典书城</strong>
<span>国学经典 历史趣闻</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
