<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=e3ce1325332e74e731416fd0&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/faedab64034f78f034c785e770310a55b2191cd1.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
霜降：一年最后的秋天
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=e3ce1325332e74e731416fd0&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
今年的霜降时间为 1...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2016-12-05</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">41</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="a212f28724b3d87e1211a29e">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=6f816236&authorId=f490c020f1d23610c8bcc521&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/54fbb2fb43166d227d3edabd4a2309f79052d24a.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>小陈茶事</strong>
<span>茶行业原创作者</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=a212f28724b3d87e1211a29e&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/83025aafa40f4bfb2045a1310e4f78f0f7361839.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
霜降已至，绿茶、红茶、白茶、武夷岩茶，养生请选它！
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=a212f28724b3d87e1211a29e&lemmaId=9380&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
霜降，是一个极有诗意的名字，从天而降的霜，让这个清冷的秋季，有了一丝丝灵动感。
从白露开始，“露凝而白”，到寒露“露气寒冷，将凝结也”，再到霜降“气肃而凝，露结为霜”，圆润的露水，到了此时，便凝成了霜花。
霜降时节，距离冬季更近一步，值此时节，气温更低，季节更替，更要注意养生。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-10-23</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">30</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
